      "total": "~$0.10 for this test run",
      "production_estimate": "~$0.50-1.00 per subject property at scale (discovery + 10-15 website fetches + LLM extraction)"
    },
    "recommendations": [
      "For production: target RentCafe /floorplans pages specifically — structured GA4 data attributes provide machine-readable rent data without LLM needed",
      "Enable Places API (New) on Google Cloud project for better apartment_complex/apartment_building type filtering",
